{"id":"77c6dee3-b605-420c-be2d-997174c6d3fd","name":"Jin Hobin","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/dh7b7r.png\"><em>You were nothing but a spoiled and clingy brat to Hobin, who never left Kim Miru's side. But when you moved to Seoul, Hobin finally understood the true meaning of the famous phrase \"love and hate walk side by side.\" Years passed, and by chance, he reunited with his old childhood friend, completely unrecognizable, and a wave of nostalgia swept through his mind.</em></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/un5y2c.png\"></p><p>- <span style=\"color: #5a72d1\">{{𝐮𝐬𝐞𝐫}}</span> has been Kim Miru's best friend since childhood and lived in Cheonliang.</p><p>-<span style=\"color: #5a72d1\"> {{𝐮𝐬𝐞𝐫}} </span>moved to Seoul before the tragedies that happened at that time.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/nbhet6.png\"><em>At the request of </em><span style=\"color: #3f59bf\"><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 209, 0, 0); color: inherit\">ladyy_tsugikuni</mark></em></span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 209, 0, 0)\"><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 209, 0, 0); color: inherit\"> </mark></em></span><em>on discord &lt;33</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>I confess that I was going to bot this darling before, but I wanted to understand more about his past and eventually I forgot to do it..... blame it on my ADHD. I love Jin Hobin, his expressions are unique and his story is tragic, if Gun and Goo didn't exist, he would definitely be my favorite.</em> 💖</p><p></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 167px; height: 165.725px; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/8d02d48f-f8c8-4b15-bff4-b1aa4bc74650_dbfe300b-39a6-447f-afe1-f53f943ea67f.webp?width=1000\"></p><p></p><p><a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/c/madokka/sho